snippet.title: Beloved ‘Golden Girl’ Betty White dies at 99 | Four 2 Five is LIVE!
snippet.description:
We’ve got the latest updates after an amber alert was issued for a teen girl missing out of Davidson County, following breaking news New Year’s Eve of the death of 99-year-old actress Betty White. 

Four 2 Five starts now!

Betty White, beloved ‘Golden Girl,’ dead at 99, according to reports: https://bit.ly/3mKcXz2
